domotic.sh: 
- copy to /etc/init.d/domotic.sh

watchdog.sh: 
- will check domotic.pid, and if process is not there but domotic.pid is, it will restart via 'domotic.sh restart'
- to install:

dirk@domotica3:~/domotic$ sudo crontab -l
# m h  dom mon dow   command
# Every minute run watchdog for domotic
* * * * *	/home/dirk/domotic/watchdog.sh >/home/dirk/domotic/cron.out
